   function and the coupled optimization variables. Thus, to tackle it, we
   propose an alternating optimization (AO) based algorithm by exploiting
   the successive convex approximation (SCA) and semidefinite relaxation
   (SDR) techniques. Simulation results show that the proposed algorithm
   can significantly improve the average rate compared with the benchmark
