   messages to multiple ground users. To improve the security performance,
   a cooperative UAV is additionally considered that transmits the jamming
   signal. In this system, we maximize the minimum secrecy rate among the
   ground users by jointly optimizing the trajectory and the transmit power
   of the UAVs as well as the user scheduling. To efficiently solve this
   nonconvex problem, we adopt block successive upper bound minimization
