Abstract = {To address the challenge of maintaining high robustness of target
   tracking in a 3D dynamic high-altitude scenario, this paper presents a
   method to formulate continuous strategic maneuvers for unmanned combat
   air vehicles (UCAVs) based on deep deterministic policy gradient (DDPG).
